{"tid":1746100,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"選舉將至，文宣重點---指去林奠度！藍黃都不滿，投保皇＝投林奠","createTime":"2019-11-22T14:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T07:47:24.000Z","uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc875118c4078c89531b5fed9a2c972a1788e7ad","tid":1746100,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藍黃最大公約數就係林奠</span></span>，就算藍絲都對其極為不滿，之前運動一開始保皇點解驚就係佢地冇得同林奠割蓆，佢又死都唔肯落台，而最近佢地終於SPIN左個波指左落示威者搞亂香港度。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以，我地最重要指出返&quot;保皇撐林奠&quot;先搞到今時今日呢個局面出黎</span></span><br />\n我未諗到一句好易明又順口亦能夠引出個MESSAGE嘅句子，以下抛磚引玉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1。建制派死撐無能林鄭，你係咪仲投票比林奠？<br />\n2。繼續投建制派林奠，抗爭者怒氣永不消，沒完沒了 <br />\n3。不投建制派，拉廢物林奠下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753f60d70d469c3948ec5b2ab61b63353ebaa7bd","tid":1746100,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"786312ded5e70b02bcabbdbe00c3c3937a80588d","tid":1746100,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:43:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5540e2aa65ecadf873e0c88bbea14e0100cfbe0b","tid":1746100,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bc9761159dcab2533a2710e4d612b6a7de9cc03","tid":1746100,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f521c2a1bddbe8c1761a01331192ef74d4fd542","tid":1746100,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63aab8dac9153316d5ee3cdd9048b8d06fbfe46d","tid